channel.description: so, im on a computer and my server workd very wel for me, but some other friends of mine cant run the server on their mac, all they get when they run the .jar file is: unable to load/download TrisidiaX cache...

item.title: Server for mac, help!
item.dc:creator: @Host_Gushers Host Gushers
item.description:
@Host_Gushers wrote:

That means that the cache couldnt be downloaded correctly…So simply go to your c drive>find the cache>make it into a .rar>send it to him>make him go to c drive>drag the .rar in there>extract>take .rar out.>Finished
